E-Commerce Website Selling Branded Second-Hand Clothing
├── Marketplace Type
│   └── E-Commerce (Online Shopping Platform)
│       └── Online thrift store offering high-quality, branded second-hand clothes, home textiles, and accessories for men, women, and kids.
├── Goals
│   ├── Affordability
│   │   └── Provide customers with premium, branded clothing and textiles at reduced prices.
│   ├── Sustainability
│   │   └── Promote eco-friendly shopping by reusing and recycling high-quality goods.
│   ├── Convenience
│   │   └── Create a seamless online shopping experience with features like secure payments, easy returns, and home delivery.
│   └── EcoPoints Program
│       └── Earn points for each purchase to redeem discounts or donate to environmental causes.
├── Quick Rough Plan / Data Schema for Marketplace
│   ├── Customer Details
│   │   ├── ID
│   │   ├── Name
│   │   ├── Email
│   │   ├── Address
│   │   └── Order History
│   ├── Product Information
│   │   ├── Product ID
│   │   ├── Name
│   │   ├── Description
│   │   ├── Price
│   │   ├── Condition
│   │   ├── Brand
│   │   ├── Category (Men/Women/Kids/Home)
│   │   ├── Images
│   │   └── Stock Availability
│   └── Add to Cart
│       ├── Order ID
│       ├── Customer ID
│       ├── Product IDs
│       └── Payment Details
├── Unique Selling Points (USPs)
│   ├── Authenticity Guaranteed
│   │   └── Verified branded items only.
│   ├── Hygiene Standards
│   │   └── Strict cleaning and quality checks before listing.
│   ├── Eco-Conscious
│   │   └── Every purchase helps reduce textile waste.
│   ├── Virtual Dressing Room
│   │   └── A feature that lets customers try outfits using AR.
│   └── Condition Grading
│       └── Transparent grading system (e.g., "Like New," "Gently Used") ensures clarity for buyers.
